name: Substantial Snag
description: Early edition from the series 'Dark Realitie' by @trnvirsingh. This artwork is another from the Sci-fi theme, which was inspired from the early 60s scifi movies. Substantial snag is the prequel of the "The Last probe' where they found the first snag on their way to the big experiment or I should say their first mistake to cross the line they shouldn't have.
